query.result:
61 He sells their flesh while it is alive;  
62 then he slaughters them like an ancient beast;  
63 many of life and of self of worth deprived.

64 Bloody exits from the sad forest;  
65 Leave it thus, that from here to a thousand years  
66 in its former state it does not become forest again.

